    WHERE c."UserId" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS c1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Description", p."ImagePath", p."Name"

SELECT c1."Id", c1."UserId", s."Id", s."Amount", s."CartId", s."OrderId", s."ProductId", s."Id0", s."Cost", s."Description", s."ImagePath", s."Name"

    SELECT c."Id", c."UserId"
    FROM "Carts" AS c
    WHERE c."UserId" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS c1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Description", p."ImagePath", p."Name"
    FROM "CartItems" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS s ON c1."Id" = s."CartId"
ORDER BY c1."Id", s."Id"

INNER JOIN "UserDeliveryInfos" AS u ON o."UserDeliveryInfoId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Amount", c."CartId", c."OrderId", c."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Description", p."ImagePath", p."Name"
    FROM "CartItems" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON c."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS s ON o."Id" = s."OrderId"
WHERE o."UserId" = @__userId_0
ORDER BY o."Id", u."Id", s."Id"

    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Description", p."ImagePath", p."Name"
    FROM "CartItems" AS c0
    INNER JOIN "Products" AS p ON c0."ProductId" = p."Id"
) AS s ON c1."Id" = s."CartId"
ORDER BY c1."Id", s."Id"

) AS c1

    SELECT c0."Id", c0."Amount", c0."CartId", c0."OrderId", c0."ProductId", p."Id" AS "Id0", p."Cost", p."Description", p."ImagePath", p."Name"
